==English==
===Etymology===
There are multiple speculative etymologies, including origination from the practice of white guys looking for black hookers in Harlem in the 1920s by honking their car horns. 

Or...the fact that blacks derogatorily consider a white's skin to be similar to a pig's skin and as a pig honks, so honky.

